room_title: Escape room "Secret Agent Man" by Let Us Go Escape Rooms in Muskegon
room_address: 200 Holton Rd Suite D Muskegon, MI 49445
room_description:
For years we’ve monitored an agent believed to be sharing secrets with the enemy. We haven’t found any concrete evidence, so it’s up to you.

We’ve hacked his phone and discovered that he will not be home for the next hour.

This is your chance Alpha team, find the proof and escape before he returns.
